In order to create reflective surfaces from flat objects, you have to apply a 3D noise map to the bump slot:

Source - Object XYZ
Offset - X:0 Y:0 Z:0
Tiling - X:1.0 Y:1.0 Z:0.1
Angle - X:0 Y:0 Z:0
Blur - 1.0
Blur offset - 0

Noise Type - Regular
Noise Threshold - High:1.0 Low:0 Levels:3 Phase:4 Size:13
Color #1 - Black
Color #2 - White
